bayedgemedia

JOIN THE CLUB
Enjoy 1st class Dining Room, Grill Room Bar & Lounge, Specialty Member Only Social events and so much more!
EXPLORE MEMBERSHIP OPTIONS
MEMBERSHIPS
We currently have 6 different memberships available. Explore all the exciting ways to become a member of Lake Jovita Golf & Country Club by choosing the membership package that works for you and your family. From a Full “Everything” Membership to a simple “Social” membership there is an option that works for you.
Membership at Lake Jovita Golf & Country Club is designed for families to enjoy the amenities and privileges of country club living. Memberships include the spouse of the primary membership holder and all unmarried children up to the age of (23) years of age still living at home. Specified memberships have access to:
Two championship golf courses
Pristine practice facilities
State-of-the-art fitness center
World class Har-Tru Clay Tennis Courts
Junior Olympic Size Swimming Pool and Sundeck
FAMILY GOLF MEMBERSHIP
$
645
00
monthly
Family Golf Membership privileges include complete access to all club amenities, Events and Championships. Membership includes the spouse of the primary membership, Children up to the age of 23 and living at home. Eligible add-ons are for parents, grandparents, and grandchildren of the primary member @ $55/mo/person.
Initiation Fee $5,000 | F&B Minimum $100/monthly or $1,400/annually
Apply Now

$

00
monthly
Single Golf Membership privileges include access to all club amenities, Events and Championships. The spouse of Single Golf Members enjoy access to all club amenities except golf.
Initiation Fee $2,500 | F&B Minimum $100/monthly or $1,400/annually
Apply Now

00
monthly
Junior Golf Memberships are available for Members under the age of 40. Membership includes the spouse, under the age of 40, of the primary membership holder and all unmarried children up to the age of 23 and living at home. Privileges include access to all club amenities, Events and Championships.
Initiation Fee $1,000 | F&B Minimum $100/monthly or $1,400/annually
Apply Now

monthly

Initiation Fee $250 | F&B Minimum $100/monthly or $1,400/annually
Apply Now

Event Booking
bayedgemedia
2025-06-20T13:42:22-04:00
EVENT BOOKING
Discover what we can do for your next event! From corporate meetings, private parties, weddings, reunions, and more we have elegant space just for you.
EXPLORE
INSPIRED EVENTS
Few places are more beautiful and accommodating than Lake Jovita Country Club. It’s been the setting for everything from weddings, corporate functions, fundraising galas, holiday parties, graduation celebrations, and more…
BOOK EARLY.
We’re already scheduling events for this fall and during the holiday season, so now is the time to reserve your spot on the calendar.
SET YOUR BUDGET.
There is typically a cost for guests, not including tax and service charge. We can accommodate budgets of around $40++ for luncheons to about $60++ for dinner & weekend events.
Prices increase during the month of December and different pricing packages for wedding events.
CHOOSE YOUR SPACE.
You can rent out the entire Club for a soiree with around 260 people or choose the intimate Private Dining Room which holds about 50 people. Our Main Dining room can easily fit about 120 people including space to set to be utilized as a dance floor.
DON’T PLAN ALONE.
Planning the perfect event can be stressful if it’s not your day job. Our in house coordinator is here to help you put all of the details together for a rememberable event.
If you would like to book an event, call 352-588-2233 ext.333 or via email at
events@lakejovita.com
